comment: * Utility class to iterate over a TLV formatted byte-array.

methods.name: public void setByteOrder(ByteOrder byteOrder)
methods.comment: * Configure the TLV iterator to use little-endian byte ordering.

methods.name: public String toString()
methods.comment:
* Prints out a parsed representation of the TLV-formatted byte array.
         * Whenever possible bytes, shorts, and integer are printed out (for
         * fields whose length is 1, 2, or 4 respectively).

methods.name: public List<byte[]> toList()
methods.comment: * Returns a List with the raw contents (no types) of the iterator.

methods.name: public Iterator<TlvElement> iterator()
methods.comment:
* Returns an iterator to step through a TLV formatted byte-array. The
         * individual elements returned by the iterator are {@link TlvElement}.
